CommunityInfo.Name: Andorra Tech & Startups
CommunityInfo.Description: Join our Technology Talks and Networking Group in Andorra! If you're passionate about technology and entrepreneurship, this is the place for you. We organize talks and networking sessions, both in-person and online, about Startups and the latest innovations in AI, Cloud Computing, Big Data, Blockchain, Open Source, WASM, and more.
